%p
  Welcome to Ghostlight Folio, #{@email}!
%p We are excited to have you join our project.
%p 
  Right now we are still in our infancy and are looking for your feedback regarding what
  features and improvements would be most useful. At the moment we have a database of 
  authors and shows, and most shows have role data associated with them. Our data is 
  still growing and improving - we welcome your additions and edits. If you would like
  to be a contributor please email us at support@ghostlightfolio.com and let us know, 
  we will be happy to add you.
%p
  For more information, you can view our
  = link_to 'About page', abouts_url
  or reach out via our
  = link_to 'Contact form', contacts_url
%p 
  A good next step after confirming your account would be to view 
  = link_to 'Shows', shows_url
  or
  = link_to 'Authors', authors_url
